Revision history for Perl extension POE::Component::YahooMessenger

0.05  Mon Dec  2 21:17:20 JST 2002
	* Fixed bug in goes_online on logon

0.04  Mon Dec  2 19:01:43 JST 2002
	- Fixed hostname typo.
	* Added socket_error handler when you can't connect to YM server
	* Added add_buddy, delete_buddy API
	- Added change_normal_status handler
	- Supported multivalue message body
	- Added cookie, group message body

0.03  Wed Sep 18 11:57:33 JST 2002
	- Renamed new_friend_alert to new_buddy_alert
	- Fixed bug in _is_buddy()
	* Added receive_file event (only works when sender is HTTP accessible)
	- Changed buddies API
	* Fixed typo in Constants.pm
	  (Thanks to Warren Lindsey <wlindsey@ponvia.com>)

0.02  Tue Sep 17 12:45:54 JST 2002
	* Fixed logon goes_online events
	- Added null message handling in receive_message

0.01  Wed Sep 11 21:24:31 2002
	- original version
